QuestData.Title: Overgrown Stone
QuestData.Description:
<A stone taken from the earthy elemental you recently defeated, covered in kelp and various other underwater plants.
You have not seen many such creatures in the deeps. Perhaps there is a story to them.
One of your new undersea allies may know more.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Show the Overgrown Stone to Finder Palta in Newhome in Nazjatar.
